CatDescriptText: Sign in background reads: "Council Calendar, Council meetings each Monday, 2:00 P.M., Thomas J. Gallagher, president...Finance Chairman: A. L. Wolk, Public Works: Bennett Rodgers, Public Service & Surveys: Paul F. Jones, Filtration & Water: John F. Counanan..."
TitMainTitle: Small crowd of women, including one on left wearing light colored coat with dark Persian lamb collar, and men, gathered in corridor outside of Pittsburgh City Council Chambers in the City County Building
